title: STK San Diego offers multiple menu categories
statement: STK San Diego provides dinner menu, market salads & starters, beverage menu, cocktails, wine, champagne, weekend brunch, and happy hour menus.

citations.quote: Dinner Menu, Market Salads & Starters, Beverage Menu, Cocktails, Wine by the Bottle, Champagne & Sparkling, Weekend Brunch Menu, All You Can Eat STK Brunch, Happy Hour Menu
